text:
Renamed CacheMixin.cache to _cache

Corrected a bug in _cache() as well: return the input function
unchanged if self.memory is None.

Added normalize_regions option to apply_roi()

This option has been added to get roi-timeseries with proper
normalisation. This is different from normalizing for variance.
See docstring for details.

Added a test for NiftiMasker

Test orientation of output of NiftiMasker.transform(), and consistency
between transform() and inverse_transform().

CacheMixin._cache always returns a Memory object.

All default 'memory' parameters have been set to Memory(cachedir=None)
for _cache() to always return a Memory() object.

Merge remote branch 'nisl/master' into api_cleanup

Conflicts:
	nisl/utils.py

Added conversion function for ROI data structures

Handling of ROI can be made using different kinds of data structures,
namely a 4D array, a list of 3D arrays, and a 3D array of labels.
Conversion functions between these formats have been written (six
functions).
